title: Works, but can be hit or miss, issues with returning items (Portugal)
text:
Editing my review. I have had no success trying to return items from Portugal. The return label never works when I go to CTT. However, Temu refunds me immediately. Be careful with ordering clothes or shoes.

â€”

Using Temu from Portugal. The app is great with sending immediate updates about shipping, up to delivery. The app also sends a lot of notifications about deals. My first order took about 10 days to arrive, but a pair of shoes I ordered was the wrong size. I also tried to print a return label, but it was not recognized by the postal company here. I was able to get a complementary refund. I think the main takeaways are to be careful about the quality of the item, and to expect it to take at least a week for shipping door-to-door and also to be careful about ordering shoes.
